<div id="review_4421906517" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4421906517" />
    <a title="Aleksandar Todorovski" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12048683-aleksandar-todorovski"><img alt="Aleksandar Todorovski" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1603984872p2/12048683.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4421906517?book_show_action=true">Dec 30, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Aleksandar Todorovski" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Aleksandar Todorovski" href="/user/show/12048683-aleksandar-todorovski">Aleksandar Todorovski</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781566635059" href="/book/show/117161.Life_at_the_Bottom">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4421906517" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15840449613010555065">A horrifying insight into the results of Social experiments and a shocking revelation about the planes of hell itself manifesting themselves in thr lives of thousands being kept in a limbo by the same crusaders of social justice claiming to protect them.<br/><br/>A tragic narrative about a once great nation of stoic , self reliable and independent people being transformed in an anti culture behemoth creeping its way towards even the highest echelons of British society.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


