<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16280863-intellectuals-and-race"><img alt="Intellectuals and Race" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1357613803l/16280863._SX98_.jpg" />
